subSection.paragraph:
The different sequences were aligned with MAFFT V7 using default parameters (
Katoh et al. 2019
). The ML [maximum-likelihood] tree was generated with IQ-TREE 2 (
Minh et al. 2020
), running with the best-fitting model TIM2 + F + G4 (
Kalyaanamoorthy et al. 2017
) and ultrafast bootstrapping (
Hoang et al. 2018
).

